Interview Tips
------------------------------------------------------------

1. Lookup = Loose relationship.
2. Master-Detail = Strong relationship.
3. Roll-Up Summary works only with Master-Detail.
4. Cascade Delete happens only in Master-Detail.
5. Many-to-Many is created using a Junction Object.
6. Hierarchical Relationship is available only on the User object.
7. Self Relationship is implemented using a Lookup on the same object.
